{"tid":1219624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無知八婆","createTime":"2019-06-13T23:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T00:05:25.000Z","uid":237459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0b7845ea650150c4848cf665591466ee36ea19","tid":1219624,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XDxYG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XDxYG0.jpg&h=9303a54e&s={SIZE}\" /> 有無佢d fd係連登可教化佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc710148ae52e5c8645e29719026ae289b10d29","tid":1219624,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/CSVP0fu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSVP0fu.png&h=0d6d5920&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0381f72e7716b68a70efd0e5ca1ec3cf72ac69f","tid":1219624,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:59:18.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊個搞亂香港經濟，一班學生何得何能呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1bede5b40c3295458253530ef44d38d64e4a75","tid":1219624,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:05:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要小看網絡平台的威力，每多一個發聲，<br />\n就多一份力量！！！</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"}]}